article_title: Scene all clear after two-car collision in Oracle
article_text:
Scene of two-car collision being cleared. (Source: Tucson News Now)

The Arizona Department of Public Safety has cleared the scene of a two-car collision near milepost 100 along Highway 77 in Oracle.

Seven people were involved, including children, but there is no word on injuries yet.

There was a helicopter on scene.
